    "Name": "Ion",
    "Details": "This arena brawler is called the Ion Raptor, named for its inventive gladiator creator, The Raptor (real name unknown). Designed in concert with Zellbringen Stables (who later went on to sell a more reasonable version named the Ion on the market), the Ion Raptor is a Clantech frankenmech in the veins of the Prometheus. Armed with a battery of six Light PPCs and four Clan-spec Streak SRM-4s and powered by a Clan XL Engine, the real innovation on the Ion Raptor is its use of Laser Heat Sinks, a rare and temperamental technology. The mech's arena record speaks for itself though, with a plethora of wins backing its weird loadout.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
